data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous condo in the sought after Battle Creek Neighborhood of St. Paul. This bright and airy home has an open floorplan with a spacious kitchen featuring plenty of countertop and cabinet space. Two bedrooms and a generous bathroom provide plenty of space. There are big windows to let the natural light in and an inviting private patio too. Unlike most condos, you have a private entrance and direct access to the attached garage. There is a convenient in-unit washer and dryer as well. Located near restaurants, shopping, parks, activities, and more. Simply move in, and enjoy.
